OL,3,CUndercover operation with Guide Dogs
OL,4,Ccharity tests Lichfield taxi drivers
OL,6,FNo drivers refused to take the fare.
OL,8,FCabinet member Cllr Alex Farrell said:
OL,9,F"This operation was organised after
OL,10,Freceiving intelligence that taxi
OL,11,Fdrivers have been refusing to carry
OL,12,Fvisually impaired people accompanied
OL,13,Fby a working guide dog.
OL,15,F"I'm pleased that all the drivers who
OL,16,Fwere checked during this operation
OL,17,Fcomplied with their legal requirement
OL,18,Fto carry guide dogs and thank them for
OL,19,Fdoing so.
