OL,6,F"Further operations are planned, and
OL,7,Fit's worth reminding drivers that if
OL,8,Fthey do refuse to carry an assistance
OL,9,Fdog, including a guide dog, they face
OL,10,Fhaving their license suspended or
OL,11,Frevoked, and prosecution.
OL,13,F"Guide dogs is a fantastic charity and
OL,14,FI'm very grateful for their support in
OL,15,Fhelping us protect the rights of
OL,16,Fvisually impaired people in Lichfield
OL,17,FDistrict."
